entries.npc_breech_1: You Black Sun Goons never give up do you? You can't buy me!
entries.dontknowyou_1: I'm sorry, friend, I don't have any business with you.
entries.otherescort_1: I'm sorry, friend, I don't have any business with you.
entries.npc_failure_1: You didn't kill him? What am I paying you for -- Oh wait, I guess I'm not.
entries.npc_noloc_1: I have a probe droid following your target. Come back in a few minutes and I should know where you can find him.
entries.npc_work_1: Haven't you taken care of this yet? You're not going soft on me are you?
entries.npc_reward_1: Here's your money, now beat it. I can't be seen associating with you disreputable types. I have my standards, you know.
entries.npc_backtowork_1: If you're not gonna go blast this guy, let me know now.
entries.npc_4_1: That's fair. How about I offer you 80% and I keep the rest as a finder's fee? Then I lie about how much money I was offered and give you the same amount I was going to in the first place? Do you want to kill this guy or not?
entries.npc_3_1: You breathe word one of this to anybody and Black Sun will burn you so quickly there won't even be any smoke.
entries.npc_2_1: I always like working with a shrewd negotiator. There's a guild mining rep that's been causing some problems for Black Sun. He's moral, upright and won't just do what he's told and take the money. His name's Jinz Finzer. Kill him.
entries.npc_1_1: Are you looking for work? I got a doozy of a job lined up that I can't do because the law is keeping a close eye on me. I figure, I get you to do this guy and we split the money. You in?
entries.npc_reset: You think you can do this later, then come see me.
entries.cantwork: You already have a job. I never hire anybody who works for someone else.
entries.next: I don't have anything else for you right now.
